{"tid":683002,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★有冇人知呢個女巴膠現況？女見習工程師：叫男同事盡情爆粗","createTime":"2018-05-29T10:33:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-30T05:16:35.000Z","uid":19454,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f96f37e7a4b7c7fb4fbf8f25a779da12f7f22bbb","tid":683002,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T10:33:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/29/181831_23d6a10372a410d431685a576adb2f57.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F29%2F181831_23d6a10372a410d431685a576adb2f57.png&h=ca1ca175&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/29/181833_5dd1a3bdbfa2af4d79f7839d4d61c7d4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F29%2F181833_5dd1a3bdbfa2af4d79f7839d4d61c7d4.png&h=b6487098&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】巴士維修工作向來是傳統「男人世界」，體重不足100磅、身高5呎多1吋「的骰」可愛女生謝穎楠（Michelle），打破傳統成為九巴創立81年以來首位女見習工程師。她<span style=\"color: red;\">入職首天因穿裙而</span>鬧笑話，惹來同事的奇怪目光，不過她不怕污糟，落手拆波箱洗引擎，證明港女修車也一樣出色。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">叫男同事盡情爆粗</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今年中入職，Michelle先被安排到荔枝角車廠的主件大修廠工作，負責維修引擎、波箱及加工零件，不過上班首天就鬧出笑話。她說，當日先到人事部報到，原以為穿着<span style=\"color: red;\">西裝裙套裝會留下好印象</span>，豈料當日已被派到車廠，「一行入維修工場，全部都係男同事，都不禁向我報以奇怪目光」。她曾怕自己「細粒」兼「論盡」拖累工作進度，但熟能生巧，近期已能獨自維修故障巴士波箱，下月調往屯門維修中心負責巴士底盤維修。<br />\n<br />\nMichelle形容自己走「女漢子」路線，在男人堆中工作照樣能埋堆，「同事初頭好顧忌，唔小心講咗粗口都會問我介唔介意，我<span style=\"color: red;\">當然叫佢哋盡情講啦</span>」。維修重型零件雖有吊臂等機器輔助，但Michelle說部份工序始終無法由她獨自進行，如調校巴士扭力用上百磅尺，同事都會主動幫忙，而她已努力多吃飯增肥。<br />\n<br />\n踏入職場四個月，身邊朋友漸覺Michelle有變化，「話我講嘢大聲，冇咁女仔，man咗」。兩年見習期，她將走遍八個工程部門工作，以熟習整部巴士設計，她希望實習完結後繼續留在九巴，累積工作經驗取得註冊工程師資格。  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20141228/18983541\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20141228%2F18983541&d=77KadedkQa3lrGK7%2FyezEUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=58d7903c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20141228%2F18983541&h=a3e97079\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20141228/18983541</a>"},{"pid":"2de7d34dbdbf3044d6a4ee845aed949713750305","tid":683002,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T10:33:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20141228/large/28la6p1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20141228%2Flarge%2F28la6p1.jpg&h=e145f006&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7202c05072b500b54320064b7191f7e66989b899","tid":683002,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T10:33:26.000Z","msg":"U like her?"},{"pid":"b99cf52095fc54a09e979ccd1db32e7f3c17944c","tid":683002,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7202c05072b500b54320064b7191f7e66989b899","tid":683002,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T10:33:26.000Z","msg":"U like her?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T10:34:52.000Z","msg":"巨乳至愛"},{"pid":"c5763832e0a637818d5b59bcba65a7555cebc8a4","tid":683002,"uid":164913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T10:35:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c2a0abceffcc939d5ee9ccba5131558475d3dd3f","tid":683002,"uid":24660,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"b99cf52095fc54a09e979ccd1db32e7f3c17944c","tid":683002,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7202c05072b500b54320064b7191f7e66989b899","tid":683002,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T10:33:26.000Z","msg":"U like her?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T10:34:52.000Z","msg":"巨乳至愛"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T10:36:02.000Z","msg":"而家我問緊你，你答巨乳做乜"}